Heidi Blickenstaff https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heidi_Blickenstaff 0 Heidi Blickenstaff (born December 28, 1971) is an actress based in New York City best known for playing a version of herself in the musical [title of show] during its Off-Broadway and Broadway runs, as well as for originating the role of Bea in the 2015 musical Something Rotten!. She co-starred with Cozi Zuehlsdorff in the Disney Channel musical version of "Freaky Friday" which was broadcast on August 10, 2018.
